snippet: Cecilia Chang, a former dean of St. John’s University, was found dead; her death is being investigated as a suicide.
abstract: Cecilia Chang, a former dean of St. John’s University, on trial for stealing more than $1 million from the school and using foreign scholarship students as her personal servants, is found dead; her death is being investigated as a suicide.

byline.original: By MOSI SECRET and WILLIAM K. RASHBAUM

lead_paragraph: Cecilia Chang, a former dean of St. John’s University, was found dead; her death is being investigated as a suicide.

headline.seo: Ex-Dean of St. John’s Is Found Dead at Home
headline.main: Ex-Dean of St. John’s, on Trial for Stealing Over $1 Million, Is Found Dead at Home
